@startuml
title State diagram for the Safehome Security Function

[*] --> Startup : Power-on

state "Startup" as Startup
state "Problem" as Problem
state "Ready" as Ready
state "Monitoring" as Monitoring
state "Alarm" as Alarm
state "Normal" as Normal

Startup --> Problem : Problem during startup
Startup --> Ready : Everything fine during startup

Problem --> [*] : Stop

Ready --> Reset : Reset
Ready --> Activate : Activate
Ready --> TurnOff : Turn off
Ready --> Monitoring : Activate monitoring

Monitoring --> Alarm : Sensor triggered
Monitoring --> Ready : False alarm or time ends

Alarm --> Normal : User enters password

Reset --> Ready : Reset
Activate --> Monitoring : Activate
TurnOff --> Ready : Turn off

Normal --> [*] : Return to normal

@enduml
